<div class="infoWrap">
<h3>
<a href="/hotel/the-mercer-new-york" class="hotel-link">The Mercer</a>
<span class="roomsInfo">
75 rooms
from <b>£534</b>
</span>
</h3>
<span class="location">New York</span>
<div class="desc">
<p>Ultimate SoHo chic. An iconic hotel, The Mercer provides the comforts of a home away from home, but in the surroundings of a trendy loft space. Artistic cool and modernist designs. Its world-class restaurant is a must.</p>
<div><b>Foodies</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;The automatic table reservation at chef Jean-Georges Vongerichten’s Mercer Kitchen is worth its weight in gold.</div><div><b>Families</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Interconnecting family suites and babysitting services.</div><div><b>Outstanding location</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Located in bustling downtown Soho.</div><div><b>Local markets</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Walk to the south-east of the hotel and you'll stumble across Little Italy and Chinatown, both well worth a visit.</div><div><b>Recommended by</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr &amp; Mrs Smith, I Escape, Tablet, Frommers, Kiwi Collection</div>
</div>
