<h3>
<a href="/hotel/the-carlyle-hotel-new-york" class="hotel-link">The Carlyle Hotel</a>
<span class="roomsInfo">
190 rooms
from <b>£553</b>
</span>
</h3>
<span class="location">New York</span>
<div class="desc">
<p>Luxurious Upper East Side landmark hotel. The Carlyle is a timeless classic and a unique place to stay discover New York Upper East Side style. Opulent suites feature exquisite views of the park and grand pianos. Keep your finger on New York's pulse.</p>
<div><b>Romantic Break</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Romantic suites, chic in house restaurants and bars and proximity to Central Park make this a perfect getaway for two.</div><div><b>City Style</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Located in the Upper East Side, with chic art deco interiors it is a New York dream</div><div><b>Traditional</b></div><div><b>Grand Hotel</b></div><div><b>Recommended by</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Tablet, Fodors, Frommers, Kiwi Collection</div>
</div>
