</h3>
<span class="location">New York State</span>
<div class="desc">
<p>Tribeca neighborhood is prime location for foodies, local explorers and relaxing in-house at the Shibui Spa and indoor pool. Modern rooms with all mod-cons. Enjoy casual Italian dining at Locanda Verde, or in the courtyard with the great bar. Perfect location for nightlife and New York!</p>
<div><b>Sights nearby</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Hop on the metro at Franklin Street and explore the city at ease.</div><div><b>Lively</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Hip and happening.</div><div><b>Local markets</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Good for local colour.</div><div><b>Full of character</b></div><div><b>Recommended by</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr &amp; Mrs Smith, Tablet</div>
